ce/Florida\", \"score\": 0.9999814924138359, \"rank\": 1.300286845218855e-05, \"text\": \"Florida\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 25-year-old Gibbs High School graduate works out every day at the YMCA in Powell as he prepares for his snowboarding competition on the world's stage in 2025.\", \"from\": 566, \"to\": 728, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 582, \"end\": 599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gibbs_High_School_(St._Petersburg,_Florida)\", \"score\": 0.954029511516694, \"rank\": 0.04818560380726045, \"text\": \"Gibbs High School\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3914\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gibbs_High_School_(St._Petersburg,_Florida)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gibbs_High_School_(St._Petersburg,_Florida)\"}, {\"begin\": 636, \"end\": 640, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YMCA\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.421495866215662e-15, \"text\": \"YMCA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YMCA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YMCA\"}, {\"begin\": 644, \"end\": 650, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicole_Powell\", \"score\": 0.998632229103062, \"rank\": 0.0013673897439133015, \"text\": \"Powell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicole_Powell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicole_Powell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Running more for cardio because constantly moving on the board, falling, pushing, getting back up definitely is a lot more tiresome than what powerlifting can be because it's one lift and you are done,\\\" said Kelly.\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 945, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 939, \"end\": 944, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\", \"score\": 0.9994219137025115, \"rank\": 0.0005784152979971683, \"text\": \"Kelly\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While Tennessee does not get a lot of snow, Kelly finds his time to prepare by going to Ober Gatlinburg when snowboarding is open for him to go.\", \"from\": 947, \"to\": 1091, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 953, \"end\": 962, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tennessee\", \"score\": 0.9232290814815074, \"rank\": 0.08309787418546098, \"text\": \"Tennessee\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tennessee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tennessee\"}, {\"begin\": 991, \"end\": 996, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\", \"score\": 0.9994219137025115, \"rank\": 0.0005784152979971683, \"text\": \"Kelly\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\"}, {\"begin\": 1035, \"end\": 1050, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ober_Gatlinburg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ober Gatlinburg\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ober_Gatlinburg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ober_Gatlinburg\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also said he watches videos on how to maximize his speed going down the courses in an effort to go for gold once again.\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1214, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Just kind of like hard work paid off, and kind of like a stress off of your shoulders,\\\" said Kelly about winning gold in 2022.\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1310, \"end\": 1315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\", \"score\": 0.9994219137025115, \"rank\": 0.0005784152979971683, \"text\": \"Kelly\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kelly said this trip to Italy will be the first time he's ever left the country, as he's admittedly a little hesitant about the long travel it'll take.\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1496, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1345, \"end\": 1350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\", \"score\": 0.9994219137025115, \"rank\": 0.0005784152979971683, \"text\": \"Kelly\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\"}, {\"begin\": 1369, \"end\": 1374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.94590021453145, \"rank\": 0.04364305321871673, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said he's most enjoyed the friends he's made over his years competing in the Special Olympics as he looks forward to his next one in March of 2025.\", \"from\": 1498, \"to\": 1648, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To help fundraise to make Kelly's trip to Italy possible you can do so by clickingthis link.\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1742, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1676, \"end\": 1681, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\", \"score\": 0.9994219137025115, \"rank\": 0.0005784152979971683, \"text\": \"Kelly\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Osbourne\"}, {\"begin\": 1692, \"end\": 1697, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.94590021453145, \"rank\": 0.04364305321871673, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resou